OL,3,CHundreds of motorists caught drink-
OL,4,Cdriving four times or more
OL,6,FHundreds of people have been caught
OL,7,Fdrink-driving at least four times,
OL,8,Fsparking calls for ministers to
OL,9,Fconsider forcing reoffenders to have
OL,10,Fbreathalysers fitted to their cars.
OL,12,FA total of 27,837 British drivers were
OL,13,Fconvicted of the offence multiple
OL,14,Ftimes in the 11 years to July 20,
OL,15,Fofficial figures obtained by the PA
OL,16,Fnews agency revealed.
OL,18,FSome 372 were caught at least four
OL,19,Ftimes, including four who were
OL,20,Fprosecuted on seven occasions.
