OL,4,Cdriving four times or more
OL,6,FThe endorsements ` which last for 11
OL,7,Fyears from the date of the offence `
OL,8,Fare given to motorists convicted of
OL,9,Fdriving or attempting to drive with
OL,10,Falcohol above legal limits.
OL,12,FMotoring organisations said the
OL,13,Ffigures demonstrate the need for the
OL,14,FGovernment to consider introducing a
OL,15,Frequirement for alcolocks to be used
OL,16,Fin the UK.
