OL,3,CHundreds of motorists caught drink-
OL,4,Cdriving four times or more
OL,6,FThe devices ` which prevent a
OL,7,Fvehicle's ignition from starting
OL,8,Funless a person passes a breath test `
OL,9,Fare used in several European nations `
OL,10,Fsuch as France, Belgium, Italy and
OL,11,FDenmark ` as a possible alternative to
OL,12,Fdriving bans.
OL,14,FRAC road safety spokesman Rod Dennis
OL,15,Fsaid: "It's chilling to see a
OL,16,Fproportion of the driving public
OL,17,Fremain intent on taking charge of a
OL,18,Fcar while intoxicated, even after
OL,19,Fthey've already been caught by the
OL,20,Fpolice on at least one occasion.
