OL,6,F"The rate of fatalities caused by
OL,7,Fpeople drinking and driving is now at
OL,8,Fa similar level to where it was in the
OL,9,Flate 1980s, so it's clear something
OL,10,Fneeds to change.
OL,12,F"Drivers need to be prevented from
OL,13,Fdrinking and driving in the first
OL,14,Fplace, so there's a good argument for
OL,15,Fmandating alcolocks be fitted to
OL,16,Fvehicles driven by anyone previously
OL,17,Fconvicted."
