OL,3,CHundreds of motorists caught drink-
OL,4,Cdriving four times or more
OL,6,FWilliam Porter, policy and
OL,7,Fcommunications manager at road safety
OL,8,Fcharity IAM RoadSmart, said: "The
OL,9,Fsheer scale of reoffending is deeply
OL,10,Ftroubling and demonstrates the need to
OL,11,Fre-evaluate our approach to reducing
OL,12,Fdrink-driving.
OL,14,F"Measures should include an expansion
OL,15,Fof drink-drive rehabilitation courses
OL,16,Fwhich lower the rate of reoffending
OL,17,Famong those who take them against
OL,18,Fthose who do not.
