OL,3,CHundreds of motorists caught drink-
OL,4,Cdriving four times or more
OL,6,F"Additionally, serious consideration
OL,7,Fshould be given to require repeat
OL,8,Foffenders to have alcolocks fitted to
OL,9,Ftheir vehicle."
OL,11,FMr Porter added: "Increasing the
OL,12,Fnumber of roadside breathalyser tests
OL,13,Fcarried out by police would also
OL,14,Fprovide a visual deterrent for those
OL,15,Fthinking about risking it."
OL,17,FPolice forces in England and Wales
OL,18,Fconducted around 229,000 breath tests
OL,19,Fin 2022, according to Home Office
OL,20,Ffigures.
