OL,6,FThe drink-drive limit in England,
OL,7,FWales and Northern Ireland is 80mg of
OL,8,Falcohol in 100ml of blood.
OL,10,FNowhere else in Europe has a limit
OL,11,Fabove 50mg/100ml.
OL,13,FThe Scottish Government reduced its
OL,14,Flimit to that level in 2014.
OL,16,FA DfT spokesperson said: "The safety
OL,17,Fof our roads is an absolute priority
OL,18,Ffor this Government. That's why we
OL,19,Fhave committed to delivering a new
OL,20,FRoad Safety Strategy ` the first in
OL,21,Fover a decade.
